US3 ‚Äî Sign on tablet: generate signature code

As a support agent
I want to generate a short code for tablet signature
So that the collaborator can sign the return form on the tablet

Description

After selecting ‚ÄúSign on tablet‚Äù and clicking Validate:
	‚Ä¢	A 2-character alphanumeric code (letter + number) is generated
	‚Ä¢	The code is communicated to the collaborator
	‚Ä¢	The screen switches to a waiting state

Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN "Sign on tablet" is selected
WHEN I click Validate
THEN a 2-character alphanumeric code is generated

THEN the code is clearly displayed on screen
AND the UI indicates that the system is waiting for tablet signature


