US7 ‚Äî Finish the process without signature (exception flow)

As a support agent
I want to finish the return process without signature
So that I can complete the process in exceptional situations

Description

A link ‚ÄúFinish the process without signature‚Äù is displayed on the signature selection screen.

Clicking it opens a confirmation modal requiring a mandatory explanation.

Acceptance Criteria

